"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gssize"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If count is 0, returns 0 and does nothing. A value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"larger than "},{"code":"G_MAXSSIZE","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will cause a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0)."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"partial result will be returned, without an error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On error -1 is returned and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" is set accordingly."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Tries to write ","type":"text"},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" bytes from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"text":" into the stream. Will block","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"during the operation."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamprotocol\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)-1i6o6"]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/CancellableRef":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/cancellableref","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GCancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" allows operations to be cancelled."}],"title":"CancellableRef"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OutputStreamProtocol":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamprotocol","abstract":[{"code":"GOutputStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a base class for implementing streaming output."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OutputStreamProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"title